 />"},{"pid":"ad189e65e95126eb9ee299d598517a66908f1129","tid":474644,"uid":143572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T11:25:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢暫時未搵到野做，一直搵緊工，佢又唔想宣假誓，有咩方法幫到佢？</blockquote><br />\n絕症就算未宣誓都拎唔到 , 你話呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絕症唔宣假誓都唔俾拎返自己d錢？！<br />\n<br />\n自己錢wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nTerminal illness, 有醫生肯簽, 短過一年命就得。"},{"pid":"74ef0daaf348e822d28ce2a3a091aa5f3720583b","tid":474644,"uid":4528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T11:25:45.000Z","msg":"唔洗諗強積金"},{"pid":"119b7ea6f9a3e7a523f890233c7dec0ee663dff8","tid":474644,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T11:29:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢暫時未搵到野做，一直搵緊工，佢又唔想宣假誓，有咩方法幫到佢？</blockquote><br />\n絕症就算未宣誓都拎唔到 , 你話呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絕症唔宣假誓都唔俾拎返自己d錢？！<br />\n<br />\n自己錢wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啲錢係啲芬佬架，65歲就有得拎架啦。"},{"pid":"cd882a2641f47b51b274441aa973f0e9a2b4059d","tid":474644,"uid":25618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T11:31:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢暫時未搵到野做，一直搵緊工，佢又唔想宣假誓，有咩方法幫到佢？</blockquote><br />\n絕症就算未宣誓都拎唔到 , 你話呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絕症唔宣假誓都唔俾拎返自己d錢？！<br />\n<br />\n自己錢wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n每個月吸你5%養班經紀ja , 未必有機會洗舊錢<br />\n<br />\n個時我老母有病一年內應該會收皮<br />\n<br />\n即刻宣誓到真係有錢到手成三四個月 , 結果真係死左都未有錢到手 , 舊錢變左拎黎做搞葬禮ja <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n都係叫你朋友諗過樣啦"},{"pid":"3379bc1fb91c3032fc9276647edd31b69d393395","tid":474644,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T11:34:49.000Z","msg":"供到有八十幾萬，點解之前份工冇做？<br />\n<br />\n俾人炒或遣散應該都拎番唔少出嚟喎。"},{"pid":"06da5075bb08066563340a2b4fc4125483570664","tid":474644,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T12:21:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2cb1909fe6186ec76dfd34041e1375c62b27df4b","tid":474644,"uid":27388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T12:43:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔攞好過攞，攞出黎又係益澳門賭場</blockquote><br />\n唔係賭錢，係人老俾人炒"},{"pid":"10f7c259a33514ea801e717489fec2e52a8db9f3","tid":474644,"uid":23315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T12:44:36.000Z","msg":"唔洗諗啦"},{"pid":"115a377eeec8c964dd9c1aab801ef78ea008c1f2","tid":474644,"uid":27388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T12:44:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>供到有八十幾萬，點解之前份工冇做？<br />\n<br />\n俾人炒或遣散應該都拎番唔少出嚟喎。</blockquote><br />\n咁就唔知有冇俾人扣，但佢收入係低微，所以強積金都唔多"},{"pid":"0eaa287f1bd77a22db7fb4dc9d124929a0ca0cc1","tid":474644,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T12:46:55.000Z","msg":"強姦金d錢唔係你架<br />\n諗其他啦<br />\n乖乖地比人姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cb4415eea158e90655f5007333d841a496649ec","tid":474644,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T13:59:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>供到有八十幾萬，點解之前份工冇做？<br />\n<br />\n俾人炒或遣散應該都拎番唔少出嚟喎。</blockquote><br />\n咁就唔知有冇俾人扣，但佢收入係低微，所以強積金都唔多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n收入低微點可以廿年唔夠有八十幾萬呀？？？？"},{"pid":"d152112f862d69fe0706e36815906d2acde0bde3","tid":474644,"uid":25618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T14:51:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>供到有八十幾萬，點解之前份工冇做？<br />\n<br />\n俾人炒或遣散應該都拎番唔少出嚟喎。</blockquote><br />\n咁就唔知有冇俾人扣，但佢收入係低微，所以強積金都唔多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n收入低微點可以廿年唔夠有八十幾萬呀？？？？</blockquote><br />\n20k 月薪 , 一個月兩份加埋供二千<br />\n<br />\n一年就24k , 廿年就480k , 計埋加人工同老強有錢賺都應該冇可能夠600k , 睇